channel.title: Frameworks
channel.description:
So my question is what's the difference between a 317 framework compared to like a 474/498 or whatever framework. Like is it just because of the client they use or is it something put into the server side. The reason for this question is that I might try to create my own framework for like 474 or 498. I'm not very good a Java but I'm going to try to see what I am capable of.
Thanks
